#   Operator: It is a Kubernetes program that "runs inside the cluster" and manages another application " automatically".

"Operator = Smart Controller"

It knows how to: 
-> install
-> update
-> fix
-> scale

Q) How does Operator Work?
-> Using "CRDs(Custom Resource Definition)"

# Prometheus Operator Flow

You write Prometheus YAML
        |
CRD understands it
        |
Operator reads it
        |
Operator creates pods, services, configs

# Security has 3 layers:

Authentication -> Authorization -> Encryption

** Authentication (Who are you?)
-> Login username
-> Login password

** Authorization (Wht can you do?)

-> Grafana Rules:
___________________________
| Role   - Permission      |
|--------|-----------------|
| Viewer - View Dashboards |
| Editor - Edit Dashboards |
| Admin  - Everything      |
----------------------------

** TLS / HTTPS 
-> TLS encrypts communitcation between browser and Grafana 

** Why Backup Dashboard?
Dashboard:
-> Took time to build
-> Represent business logic

If deleted  = loss

** Beginner backup steps: 
Steps: 
-> Open grafana
-> Open dashboard
-> Export -> JSON
-> Save file

** Restore Steps:
-> Open Granfana
-> Import dashboard
-> Upload JSON
-> Dashboard restored
